✅ The answer is YES! ⁣ Cucumbers does have an effect on our skin care routine.⁣ ⁣ ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
ℹ️ One of its many benefits is that it contains vitamin C and caffeic acid, two antioxidants that, when applied to skin, help fend off wrinkles, sun damage and more. Cucumbers can also control puffiness of your eyes. Next time when you feel tired, try putting a chilled slice of cucumber on your eyes and let it rest for 10-15 minutes. ⁣ ⁣It is a great way to refresh your eyes.⁣ ⁣ ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
